<p>
      <b> Click on the buttons below to change
       the language of the webpage. /
        Haga clic en los botones a continuación para cambiar
        el idioma de la página web.
        </b>
   </p>
   <!-- Define the buttons that will
           change the language of the page
 and reload it -->
   <button onclick="changeLanguage('eng')">
   Change to English</button>
          <button onclick="changeLanguage('es')">
       Change to Spanish
   </button>
   <!-- Define the content of the page
                      that would be changed -->
   <p id="siteContent">
     Welcome, this website is to help give greater accessibility to education in our communities as many
     people don't have the required amount of education for our society for the working field.
      We believe that this is an inequity that is overlooked, even though there are many people
      in our lives who have lived through this inequity. As it creates an imbalance in the equality
       of those who need a job. So our goal is to support those who couldn't gain that type of
        education and help try to prevent it from happening to others.
   </p>
   <script>
       // Create a function to change
       // the hash value of the page
       function changeLanguage(lang) {
           location.hash = lang;
           location.reload();
       }
       // Define the language reload anchors
       let language = {
           eng: {
               welcome:
                   "Portal! You can choose any language " +
                   "using the buttons above!"
           },
           es: {
               welcome:"Bienvenido, este sitio web es para ayudar a brindar mayor accesibilidad a la educación en nuestras comunidades, ya que muchas personas no tienen la cantidad de educación requerida por nuestra sociedad para el campo laboral. Creemos que esta es una inequidad que se pasa por alto, a pesar de que hay muchas personas en nuestras vidas que han vivido esta inequidad. Ya que crea un desequilibrio en la igualdad de quienes necesitan un trabajo. Entonces, nuestro objetivo es apoyar a aquellos que no pudieron obtener ese tipo de educación y ayudar a tratar de evitar que les suceda a otros."
           }
       };
       // Check if a hash value exists in the URL
       if (window.location.hash) {
           // Set the content of the webpage
           // depending on the hash value
           if (window.location.hash == "#es") {
               siteContent.textContent =
                   language.es.welcome;
                 
           }
       }
   </script>




      <p>
